{"title":"微信小程序获得服务器ip","date":"2018-07-03T02:53:00.000Z","link":"post/134","categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:16:58.737Z","content":"<p>错误：<br>    有时候在小程序前端能取到图片的地址，但是不显示<br>解决方法：<br>    可能是数据库中只存了图片的服务器地址，但是地址不全<br>    例：<br>    <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>但如果要显示到页面上需要加ip。即：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">192.168.100.103/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>即在前端：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;image src=&apos;&#123;&#123;attachment&#125;&#125;&#123;&#123;item.static_image&#125;&#125;&apos;&gt;&lt;/image&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>后台js：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var t = getApp(),</span><br><span class=\"line\">  a = t.requirejs(&quot;core&quot;),</span><br><span class=\"line\">  e = (t.requirejs(&quot;icons&quot;), t.requirejs(&quot;wxParse/wxParse&quot;));</span><br><span class=\"line\">Page(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  data: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    attachment: t.globalData.attachment</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>在微信小程序中定义全局变量：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">globalData: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   rencent_order_time_before: 30,//最近订单中往前显示订单的时间</span><br><span class=\"line\">   custom_service_phonenumber: &quot;023-5519827&quot;,//客服电话</span><br><span class=\"line\">   appid: &quot;wx68c04a444055058c&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   api: &quot;http://192.168.100.12:8080/app/ewei_shopv2_api.php?i=1&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   approot: &quot;http://192.168.100.12:8080/addons/ewei_shopv2/&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   attachment: &quot;http://192.168.100.12:8080/attachment/&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">   userInfo: null</span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"php 小数整理,向上取整,向下去整,四舍五入,丢弃小数部分,保留整数部分","link":"post/135"},"next":{"title":"数据库在新建表的时候添加注释comment on column","link":"post/133"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/134/"}